title: CBT Nuggets Windows 8 70-687
description:
This Microsoft Windows 8 training series with James Conrad covers installing and configuring Windows 8.

Recommended skills:

    Familiarity with Microsoft OS

Take on Windows 8 with this series from trainer James Conrad!
